    "answer_id" : 79781870,
    "question_id" : 70604368,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>It is possible to declare the access level on all log annotations, including <code>@Slf4j</code>, since Lombok 1.18.42, using <a href=\"https://projectlombok.org/api/lombok/extern/slf4j/Slf4j#access()\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://projectlombok.org/api/lombok/extern/slf4j/Slf4j#access()</a></p>\n"
  } ],
